<p><strong>What is the naughty list?</strong></p>
<p>Your Naughty list is the place you put people with whom you don't wish to share the Christmas spirit - you won't see their posts and they won't see yours (They won't know they're on your list)<br /><br />
<em>Disclaimer: Just because they are on your naughty list, doesn't mean they are on Santa's.</em></p>